    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324760/extras/50c7a42c2b434b02abf40637e3b8de5d.avif?t=1762963051\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to <strong>FLORIDA INTERSTATE '86</strong>, a light-weight driving game where the goal is to cruise into the sunset for as long as possible while earning points by collecting cassette tapes and driving dangerously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324760/extras/e8991ffb22b6885e67e5dec3c11568c9.poster.avif?t=1762963051\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324760/extras/e8991ffb22b6885e67e5dec3c11568c9.webm?t=1762963051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324760/extras/e8991ffb22b6885e67e5dec3c11568c9.mp4?t=1762963051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dynamic noon-sunset lighting system, a selection of colorful retro-styled sports cars and a synthwave/chillwave soundtrack ensure that every single one of your trips into this '80s fantasy Sunshine State is a unique one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324760/extras/d37084b0e901026a86c9616b0b7000d0.poster.avif?t=1762963051\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324760/extras/d37084b0e901026a86c9616b0b7000d0.webm?t=1762963051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"ht